title: Joey Logano wins Talladega with controversial finish that
text:
> North Carolina Joey Logano wins Talladega with controversial finish that Tony Stewart (14) crashes with Denny Hamlin (11), Austin Dillon (3), Jimmie Johnson (48) and others on a restart attempt in the final laps of the NASCAR Sprint Cup Series auto race at Talladega Superspeedway, Sunday, Oct. 25, 2015, in Talladega, Ala. (AP Photo/ Mark Almond) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
